item.title: About me
item.description: Hello World! Welcome to my website! I’m Mateusz Konat, a passionate tech tinkerer eager to share my journey with you. Here, you’ll discover more about me and my activities, explore my blog, and dive into my projects. Also, you can easily navigate through the content of interest on my website using the tags at the top of each page (indicated by “#” sign like “#my projects” or “#creativity”). Now, let me tell you more about myself!
